modRewriteHelp.nginx:
API Fout: EspoCRM API unavailable.<br> Toevoegen this code to Nginx Host Config (inside "server" block):<br>
<pre>
location /api/v1/ {
    if (!-e $request_filename){
        rewrite ^/api/v1/(.*)$ /api/v1/index.php last; break;
    }
}

location / {
    rewrite reset/?$ reset.html break;
}</pre>
